# Enigma Sentinel

Enigma Sentinel provides advanced security monitoring and anomaly detection across Insider platform.

## Key Features
- Real-time security monitoring
- Anomaly detection and alerting
- User behavior analytics
- Threat intelligence integration
- Security event logging and reporting

## Testing Requirements

### Core Functionality
- Security event detection accuracy
- Alert triggering and notifications
- User behavior pattern analysis
- Threat detection algorithms
- Event correlation logic

### UI/UX Requirements
- Security dashboard visualization
- Alert management interface
- Event timeline and filtering
- Investigation tools
- Report generation

### Data Validation
- Security metric calculations
- Alert threshold accuracy
- Event correlation correctness
- Threat scoring algorithms

## Common Issues to Test
1. False positive alerts
2. Missed security events
3. Alert notification failures
4. Dashboard data inconsistencies
5. Event correlation errors
